### Register user (direct user-service)
POST {{user_service_url}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "username": "referral.user.01",
  "email": "referral.user.01@example.com",
  "firstName": "Referral",
  "lastName": "User",
  "password": "Secure@1234",
  "role": "USER",
  "active": true
}

### Login user (direct user-service) - copy access_token into @token
POST {{user_service_url}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "username": "referral.user.01",
  "password": "Secure@1234"
}

### Create referral code for current user (direct service)
POST {{base_url}}/referrals/me/code
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get current user referral code (direct service)
GET {{base_url}}/referrals/me/code
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Validate referral code (direct service)
GET {{base_url}}/referrals/validate?code=REF69AC02OV

### Create referral code via gateway
POST {{gateway_url}}/referrals/me/code
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get referral code via gateway
GET {{gateway_url}}/referrals/me/code
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
